 places visited, people met, what stood out. Names, dates, and the personal moments that make this trip yours.\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Heading\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"level\\\":2},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"\\ud83d\\udcb0 From your cost spreadsheet (trip-costs.xlsx)\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Line-by-line costs across the trip \\u2014 flights, accommodation, park fees, safari, and extras. This is your budget ground truth, and it has specific figures that matter for the safari balance payment.\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Heading\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"level\\\":2},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"\\ud83c\\udfde\\ufe0f From the Ngorongoro park-fee PDF\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Official conservation-area tariffs \\u2014 entry fees, vehicle fees, and any ranger-related charges. This is the official reference for what you should expect to pay at the crater.\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Heading\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"level\\\":2},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"\\ud83d\\udcf8 From your Stone Town photo\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"A low-angle view looking up into the courtyard of a multi-story building with white stucco walls and Middle Eastern/Spanish-style architectural details. The scene shows several stacked dark wooden balconies with ornate carved railings, arched windows, and wooden shutters, some open. The building rises around a narrow open-air space under a bright blue sky, with strong sunlight creating sharp shadows. A striped awning and a wall-mounted lamp are visible on the left, and the overall impression is of an elegant historic hotel, residence, or courtyard complex with decorative, traditional design elements.\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Heading\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"level\\\":2},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"\\ud83c\\udf99\\ufe0f From your crater-day voice memo\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Your driver-guide